       "ReferenceSDDocumentItem"                 as "SalesQuotationItem",
       sum("NetAmount")                          as "CnvtSalesQuotationAmount",
       sum( "RequestedQuantityInBaseUnit")       as "CnvtSalesQuotationQuantity",
       sum("NETAMOUNT_CC_CUR")                   as "CnvtSalesQuotationAmount_CC_CUR"
       from "SAP_SD_HL_SalesDocumentItem_V2"
       where "ReferenceSDDocumentCategory" = 'B'AND
              "SDDocumentCategory"= 'C'
